headline: US oil futures inch higher as API inventory shows smaller increase in crude stocks
summary: Investing.com -- U.S. crude oil futures inched slightly above post-settlement levels Tuesday after the American Petroleum Institute showed a smaller-than-expected increase in U.S. weekly crude supplies.

headline: Is Colgate-Palmolive Stock Underperforming the S&P 500?
summary: Colgate-Palmolive has underperformed the broader market over the past year, but Wall Street analysts maintain a reasonably upbeat outlook for the stock.
